(5) To use a pesticide at any dosage, concentration, or frequency greater
than specified or recommended on the labeling unless the labeling allows the
greater dosage, concentration, or frequency;

(6) To handle, transport, store, display, or distribute a pesticide
in a manner that violates any provision of the Pesticide Act or a rule or
regulation adopted and promulgated under the act;

